Method Detail

backTranslate

public DNASeq backTranslate(GeneticCode myGC)
Creates a new DNA sequence from a protein by back translation of the protein sequence. The back translation gives usually multiple choices given the degeneration of genetic code. So the newly created DNA sequence is degenerated.

Parameters:
myGC - is the genetic code used in the back translation process.
